268
00:17:16.423 --> 00:17:18.017
Somebody might be hurt.

269
00:17:20.226 --> 00:17:23.359
- RAY: What are you doing?
- FRANK: I'm gonna check it out.

270
00:17:27.133 --> 00:17:29.557
RAY: You guys doing the Mother Teresa Show?

271
00:17:29.637 --> 00:17:31.346
Wait.

272
00:18:01.602 --> 00:18:02.946
JOHN: Nothing down here.

273
00:18:28.597 --> 00:18:29.770
