281
00:19:28.824 --> 00:19:31.501
There's no service
in this shit-hole part of town.

282
00:19:32.328 --> 00:19:34.321
Let's get him to an emergency room.

283
00:19:36.667 --> 00:19:38.342
How do you work this?

284
00:19:42.205 --> 00:19:44.928
I didn't see him. He came out of nowhere.

285
00:19:45.008 --> 00:19:46.512
It wasn't my fault.

286
00:19:48.779 --> 00:19:51.159
Hey. bring him into the RV.

287
00:20:07.931 --> 00:20:10.038
RAY: Is he okay?

288
00:20:14.871 --> 00:20:17.787
Easy. Careful.

289
00:20:31.356 --> 00:20:33.064
Get a towel.

290
00:20:37.962 --> 00:20:39.637
RAY: He's been shot.

291
00:20:41.098 --> 00:20:42.271
Put this under his...

292
00:20:44.001 --> 00:20:46.530
Careful. Easy.

293
00:20:54.846 --> 00:20:56.258
He's a thief.

294
00:20:56.914 --> 00:20:59.504
The cops probably shot him.
They'll be back any minute.

295
00:20:59.584 --> 00:21:00.806
Who shot you?

296
00:21:00.886 --> 00:21:02.040
Leave him alone.

297
00:21:02.120 --> 00:21:03.876
Goddamn it. somebody shot him!

298
00:21:03.956 --> 00:21:05.611
We could all be in danger.

299
00:21:05.691 --> 00:21:07.280
We're not leaving him here.

300
00:21:07.360 --> 00:21:09.515
I've had a lot to drink tonight.

301
00:21:09.595 --> 00:21:12.351
What's your problem? The kid is hurt.

302
00:21:12.431 --> 00:21:14.687
