305
00:21:19.772 --> 00:21:22.728
- We won't let anybody hurt you.
- Get me out of here!

306
00:21:22.808 --> 00:21:26.799
Shut up! Goddamn it!
I can't hear myself think!

307
00:21:26.879 --> 00:21:29.402
Who the hell are you telling to shut up?

308
00:21:29.482 --> 00:21:30.569
Listen.

309
00:21:30.649 --> 00:21:33.272
