319
00:22:05.151 --> 00:22:10.076
Hey. help! Police! We got somebody shot!

320
00:22:10.156 --> 00:22:11.626
MIKE: They turned the corner.

321
00:22:22.769 --> 00:22:23.857
Take it easy.

322
00:22:23.937 --> 00:22:25.236
Where the hell are they?

323
00:22:57.938 --> 00:23:00.194
MIKE: Ray. you okay?

324
00:23:00.274 --> 00:23:01.962
RAY: I'm all right. You all right. Frank?

325
00:23:02.042 --> 00:23:03.215
Yeah.

326
00:23:25.601 --> 00:23:26.755
