328
00:23:28.704 --> 00:23:31.660
Probably some no-insurance.
car-driving asshole...

329
00:23:31.740 --> 00:23:34.018
bashed into us in a fucking junker.

330
00:23:35.411 --> 00:23:37.399
Un-fucking-believable.

331
00:23:37.479 --> 00:23:39.757
