338
00:24:05.174 --> 00:24:06.929
We're stuck in here.

339
00:24:07.009 --> 00:24:08.498
We're stuck. okay?

340
00:24:08.578 --> 00:24:10.967
We're stuck in this piece of shit
which I now own!

341
00:24:11.047 --> 00:24:13.279
This piece of fucking shit!

342
00:24:15.785 --> 00:24:17.015
Calm down!

343
