- MIKE: Then find it.

362
00:25:22.220 --> 00:25:24.309
RAY: It's got to be somewhere around here.

363
00:25:24.389 --> 00:25:26.382
- MIKE: Look for it.
- RAY: I'm looking. man.

364
00:25:41.740 --> 00:25:42.879
MIKE: You see anything?

365
00:25:45.677 --> 00:25:46.850
Nothing.

366
00:25:54.052 --> 00:25:55.140
