367
00:25:55.220 --> 00:25:56.599
We can all squeeze through there...

368
00:25:57.923 --> 00:25:59.612
MAN: What up. Teddy? Playing hide-and-seek?

369
00:25:59.692 --> 00:26:02.315
Come on out. Come here. motherfucker.

370
00:26:02.395 --> 00:26:05.709
Back the fuck off. please.

371
00:26:07.266 --> 00:26:08.688
