372
00:26:08.768 --> 00:26:10.066
You want to keep him?

373
00:26:12.237 --> 00:26:14.026
Back off. You ain't got no balls.

374
00:26:14.106 --> 00:26:17.897
You children sit tight.
and no one will get hurt.

375
00:26:17.977 --> 00:26:19.424
Crack a window.

376
