406
00:27:56.678 --> 00:28:01.437
Did you mention my name
to the guys in the truck?

407
00:28:01.517 --> 00:28:04.072
I didn't say anything.

408
00:28:04.152 --> 00:28:06.225
I wouldn't rat you out or say shit!

409
00:28:08.357 --> 00:28:10.946
So you want me to let you go?

410
00:28:11.026 --> 00:28:13.716
Then I'm supposed to
conduct business on the street?

411
00:28:13.796 --> 00:28:15.784
Who's going to know. right?

412
00:28:15.864 --> 00:28:17.553
Nobody's going to tell.

413
00:28:17.633 --> 00:28:19.489
- He's not gonna tell. I'm not.
- That's right.

414
00:28:19.569 --> 00:28:22.040
No! Come on! All you got to do is...

415
00:28:25.173 --> 00:28:27.041
(GUNSHOTS CONTINUE)

416
00:28:41.857 --> 00:28:44.899
