- How many guys in the truck?

417
00:28:45.729 --> 00:28:47.216
About four.

418
00:28:47.296 --> 00:28:50.287
North Shore plates. too. Just great.

419
00:28:50.367 --> 00:28:53.863
Well. boys. rule number two: no witnesses.

420
00:28:58.975 --> 00:29:00.319
Come on!

421
00:29:03.013 --> 00:29:04.186
We're next!

422
00:29:25.936 --> 00:29:27.191
