Where do these guys think they're going?

425
00:29:36.748 --> 00:29:38.126
(GUNSHOTS)

426
00:30:16.822 --> 00:30:17.995
FRANK: Shit.

427
00:30:20.659 --> 00:30:22.080
Sorry. man.

428
00:30:22.160 --> 00:30:23.937
It's not what I had in mind.

429
00:30:26.298 --> 00:30:28.354
Thanks. That's what I'll tell the dealer.

430
00:30:28.434 --> 00:30:31.866
MIKE: You won't be telling him nothing
unless we get out of here.

431
00:30:32.905 --> 00:30:35.261
FALLON: That was great. Do it again.

432
00:30:35.341 --> 00:30:36.428
That's not funny.

433
00:30:36.508 --> 00:30:38.931
Hey. man. that was funny.

434
00:30:39.011 --> 00:30:41.540
Shit looks like the Hindenburg. Come on.

435
00:31:13.012 --> 00:31:14.185
FRANK: Let's go. Ray.

436
00:31:40.240 --> 00:31:41.414
RAY: Stop.

437
00:31:45.379 --> 00:31:46.723
