438
00:31:51.752 --> 00:31:53.674
John. you all right?

439
00:31:53.754 --> 00:31:55.643
Why? Why'd they do it?

440
00:31:55.723 --> 00:31:57.135
They killed him.

441
00:32:00.928 --> 00:32:03.423
I don't think they'll follow us.
They won't do that.

442
00:32:04.465 --> 00:32:07.597
We saw them shoot that kid.
We were witnesses.

443
00:32:10.771 --> 00:32:12.366
Where the hell are we?

444
00:32:15.544 --> 00:32:17.499
MIKE: Why'd you get off the expressway?

445
00:32:17.579 --> 00:32:19.801
Are we at the blaming stage now?

446
00:32:19.881 --> 00:32:22.797
I don't remember twisting your arm
to get off the expressway.

447
00:32:26.287 --> 00:32:27.791
(TIRES SQUEAL)

448
00:33:21.344 --> 00:33:23.266
FRANK: Did they see us?

449
00:33:23.346 --> 00:33:25.840
I don't know. I don't think so.

450
00:33:41.865 --> 00:33:43.020
RAY: Frank was right.

451
00:33:43.100 --> 00:33:45.489
- They do want to kill us.
- I never said that.

452
00:33:45.569 --> 00:33:47.733
- What are we gonna do?
- Shut up.

453
00:33:52.876 --> 00:33:54.532
Look what the cat drug in.

454
00:33:54.612 --> 00:33:56.066
MIKE: Keep your voice down.

455
00:33:56.146 --> 00:33:57.650
FALLON: Hello. ladies.

456
00:33:58.649 --> 00:34:00.392
What do you think of the neighborhood?

457
00:34:01.885 --> 00:34:03.774
(THUD)

458
00:34:03.854 --> 00:34:07.811
