like the goddamn Avon lady.

465
00:34:30.848 --> 00:34:34.425
By the way. you fucked up my car...

466
00:34:35.420 --> 00:34:36.923
and I don't have collision.

467
00:34:38.255 --> 00:34:44.098
Guy sounds like he wants to
do you bodily harm or something.

468
00:34:47.532 --> 00:34:50.021
I'm a college graduate.

469
00:34:50.101 --> 00:34:51.389
FIRST BUM: That's Buck.

470
00:34:51.469 --> 00:34:53.815
He's got the brain of a chicken.

471
00:34:56.508 --> 00:34:59.390
Sure would be a shame
if he heard you in here!

472
00:35:02.581 --> 00:35:04.289
Damn shame.

473
00:35:07.853 --> 00:35:10.643
They'd shoot us and then blow your heads off.

474
00:35:10.723 --> 00:35:12.466
I don't think so.

475
00:35:13.459 --> 00:35:17.639
Might even be grateful.
Might give us a reward.

476
00:35:19.865 --> 00:35:24.284
All right. goddamn it. Name your price.

477
00:35:27.005 --> 00:35:32.119
Gee. Mr. Businessman.
what did you have in mind?

478
00:35:37.383 --> 00:35:38.556
FALLON: Don't move!

479
00:35:41.621 --> 00:35:43.158
Don't whisper.

480
00:35:44.825 --> 00:35:46.818
Don't even breathe.

481
00:35:49.996 --> 00:35:51.500
(THUD)

482
00:35:53.834 --> 00:35:58.858
Don't you hate it when you try to be quiet.

483
00:35:58.938 --> 00:36:06.649
