amplified 20 or 30 times?

484
00:36:11.084 --> 00:36:12.280
What is that?

485
00:36:14.655 --> 00:36:15.809
What's that smell?

486
00:36:15.889 --> 00:36:17.484
You guys wearing cologne?

487
00:36:17.591 --> 00:36:20.085
Or is that fear?

488
00:36:29.871 --> 00:36:33.083
- FIRST BUM: Nice watch.
- RAY: Go to hell.

489
00:36:35.410 --> 00:36:37.298
