490
00:36:37.378 --> 00:36:40.054
Ray. give it to him.

491
00:37:00.402 --> 00:37:02.490
(SCRAPING)

492
00:37:02.570 --> 00:37:04.973
(CLACKING)

493
00:37:08.075 --> 00:37:10.423
(BANGING ON SIDE OF TRAIN)

494
00:37:11.680 --> 00:37:13.769
