495
00:37:13.849 --> 00:37:15.387
I'm home!

496
00:37:16.685 --> 00:37:18.758
You got some explaining to do.

497
00:37:38.106 --> 00:37:39.610
Don't touch me.

498
00:37:42.077 --> 00:37:43.706
Don't be stupid. John.

499
00:38:14.344 --> 00:38:15.415
It's all I got.

500
00:38:25.254 --> 00:38:28.912
