starting to piss me off.

501
00:38:28.992 --> 00:38:31.415
This is eating into my drinking time.

502
00:38:31.495 --> 00:38:33.384
Tell you what I'm gonna do.

503
00:38:33.464 --> 00:38:37.621
Since I'm a nice person and
in touch with my inner child...

504
00:38:37.701 --> 00:38:39.257
I'll give you a chance.

505
00:38:39.337 --> 00:38:44.094
Come out. forget the bullshit.
and we'll discuss this.

506
00:38:44.174 --> 00:38:45.621
I'm going to count to three.

507
00:38:47.177 --> 00:38:49.600
One Mississippi...

508
00:38:49.680 --> 00:38:52.994
two Mississippi...

509
00:38:59.256 --> 00:39:02.696
